    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Swietenia macrophylla, native to areas in southern North America, Central and South America. It has been introduced for cultivation in Asia. The wood is used for cabinet-making and other purposes.</Note_Text>
